    <h2>The Problem</h2>
    <p>Dental offices often struggle with inaccurate inventory tracking. This leads to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Overstocking and wasted expired supplies</li>
      <li>Stockouts of essential items</li>
      <li>Time wasted on manual inventory checks</li>
      <li>Lack of visibility into inventory levels and usage</li>
    </ul>
    <p>These issues impact efficiency, cost, and even patient care.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>The Solution</h2>
    <p>Our AI-powered inventory management system provides:</p>
